HEADWORD: Recorporification
<hw>Re`cor*por`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(r?`k?r*p?r`?*f?*k?"sh?n)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of investing again with a body; the state of
